cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with object recognition using deep learning and sensorimotor information. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of neural networks for fusing information sources suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
